==English==

===Etymology===
From [[god]] + [[child]]

===Noun===
{{en-noun-irreg|godchildren}}

# A [[child]] whose [[baptism]] is sponsored by a [[godparent]].  In some cases the relationship is maintained indefinitly, with the godchild being treated much like a niece or nephew.

